Thread starter cletusSamboy Start date Sep 24, 2022 1 2 Next C cletusSamboy Bluelighter Joined Oct 24, 2021 Messages 420 Sep 24, 2022 #1 After performing an acetone wash on 0.5g and getting back 0.5g back I decided to powder up the shards and dump it in store bought iso alcohol. It says 100% pure but probably more like 91%. After stirring for a minute and letting sit for 5 minutes to let any undissolved product settle I carefully poured out the alcohol into another jar. After evaporating the iso from the first jar I was left with 0.3g. After evaporating the iso from the second jar I was left with 0.2g. Smoking some from the first jar produced a small amount of vapor with giving some moderate effect while the product from the second jar produced a much thicker and kinda sweet smelling vapor with much stronger effects. My conclusion is I think iso with a small amount of water separated a lot of the meth from another cut that acetone wouldn't remove. I've tried this on another batch getting similar results. The undissolved product giving off a light airy odorless vapor and the dissolved giving off a much thicker and longer lasting vapor with a sweetish kinda smell. ¬† Last edited: Nov 5, 2022 Reactions: BK38, G_Chem and SuperPsych LucidSDreamr Bluelighter Joined May 23, 2013 Messages 7,457 Sep 24, 2022 #2 If you try it with iso at very cold temperatures you might even get cleaner product but possibly less. ¬† Reactions: G_Chem iheartsleep Greenlighter Joined Nov 3, 2022 Messages 3 Nov 3, 2022 #3 This sounds interesting, how are you sure it is "condensing" and not just being destroyed/lost?
